<p><a href="/docs/iii">iii</a> is a new platform which allows scripts to be run on grids and arcs, connecting directly to synths via usb-MIDI. it's available free as an firmware update to recent-ish rp2040-based hardware.</p>
<p>shown above, the script <a href="/docs/iii/library/wake">wake</a> playing <a href="https://atrium.whimsicalraps.com">atrium</a>.</p>
